data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The site gives us solid constraints: cream and paper surfaces, charcoal rules, coral CTAs, editorial serif headlines, clean sans UI, and the business promise “preview before payment.” I’m going to treat the page as an email design system showcase rather than a generic landing page: four rendered email examples plus a concrete component handoff."}

