data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_10","content":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"> <head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"profitslocal logo, color, typography, and design reference assets.\"><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/brand/logo-mark.svg\" type=\"image/svg+xml\"><title>Brand assets - profitslocal</title><script src=\"/funnel-context.js\" defer></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_astro/Layout.D4Qyln4D.css\"></head> <body> <div class=\"page-shell\"> <header class=\"topbar\"> <nav class=\"nav\" aria-label=\"Primary navigation\"> <a class=\"brand\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"profitslocal home\"> <img src=\"/brand/logo-horizontal.svg\" alt=\"profitslocal\"> </a> <div class=\"nav-links\"> <a href=\"/#process\">How it works</a><a href=\"/#pricing\">Pricing</a><a href=\"/#faq\">FAQ</a><a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a href=\"/#contact\">Contact</a> </div> <a class=\"nav-cta\" href=\"/#contact\">Send a brief</a> </nav> </header> <main>  <section class=\"poster-section brand-assets-page\"> <div class=\"brand-assets-hero\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Brand reference</p> <h1>profitslocal brand assets.</h1> <p class=\"lede\">The original design reference page for the profitslocal identity: logo direction, Local Intelligence Collage, color system, type, and generated website-section references.</p> </div> <div class=\"brand-assets-logo-card\"> <img src=\"/brand/logo-horizontal.svg\" alt=\"profitslocal horizontal logo\"> <p>Research first. Design with taste. Preview before payment.</p> </div> </div> <div class=\"brand-assets-grid\"> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel logo-panel\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Logo</p> <div class=\"logo-lockups\"> <div> <img src=\"/brand/logo-mark.svg\" alt=\"profitslocal logo mark\"> <span>Mark</span> </div> <div> <img src=\"/brand/logo-horizontal.svg\" alt=\"profitslocal horizontal logo\"> <span>Horizontal</span> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Brand essence</p> <h2>Beautiful, research-backed local-business websites, pre-built before you pay.</h2> <p class=\"micro\">profitslocal should feel like a creative research lab for local-business websites: warm, fast, trustworthy, artistic, and practical.</p> </section> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel wide\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Color system</p> <div class=\"color-grid\"> <article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #FFF6EC\"></span> <b>Cream</b> <code>#FFF6EC</code> <p>Main warm background</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #FFFCF7\"></span> <b>Paper</b> <code>#FFFCF7</code> <p>Cards, notes, panels</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #17191C\"></span> <b>Charcoal</b> <code>#17191C</code> <p>Main text and rules</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #5E6268\"></span> <b>Muted</b> <code>#5E6268</code> <p>Body copy</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #FF5A3D\"></span> <b>Coral</b> <code>#FF5A3D</code> <p>CTA, logo mark, accents</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #FFB39F\"></span> <b>Coral soft</b> <code>#FFB39F</code> <p>Soft highlights</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #FFE1CE\"></span> <b>Peach</b> <code>#FFE1CE</code> <p>Warm section surfaces</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #FFD45A\"></span> <b>Citrus</b> <code>#FFD45A</code> <p>Growth and optimism</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #CDECCF\"></span> <b>Mint</b> <code>#CDECCF</code> <p>Trust and success cues</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #47B86A\"></span> <b>Green</b> <code>#47B86A</code> <p>Positive metrics</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #8BD3F7\"></span> <b>Sky</b> <code>#8BD3F7</code> <p>Motion and annotations</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #327BEA\"></span> <b>Blue</b> <code>#327BEA</code> <p>Search and data cards</p> </article><article class=\"color-chip\"> <span style=\"background: #EADCFB\"></span> <b>Lilac soft</b> <code>#EADCFB</code> <p>Creative accent</p> </article> </div> </section> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel type-panel\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Typography</p> <div> <h2>Editorial serif headlines.</h2> <p>Clean sans body copy for forms, buttons, labels, and product surfaces.</p> </div> <div> <h3>Display</h3> <p>Playfair Display, Libre Baskerville, Cormorant Garamond, Georgia</p> </div> <div> <h3>UI / body</h3> <p>Inter, Manrope, Plus Jakarta Sans, system-ui</p> </div> </section> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Design language</p> <h2>Local Intelligence Collage.</h2> <p class=\"micro\">Warm cream surfaces, coral CTA energy, maps, storefront worlds, browser previews, research notes, annotation marks, and optimistic growth cues.</p> </section> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel wide\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Reference images</p> <div class=\"reference-grid\"> <a href=\"/brand/images/section-01-hero.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-01-hero.png\" alt=\"Hero brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Hero</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-02-research.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-02-research.png\" alt=\"Research brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Research</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-03-taste-strategy.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-03-taste-strategy.png\" alt=\"Taste strategy brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Taste strategy</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-04-preview-gallery.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-04-preview-gallery.png\" alt=\"Preview gallery brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Preview gallery</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-05-transparent-pricing.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-05-transparent-pricing.png\" alt=\"Pricing brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Pricing</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-06-performance-seo.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-06-performance-seo.png\" alt=\"Performance brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Performance</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-07-process.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-07-process.png\" alt=\"Process brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Process</span> </a><a href=\"/brand/images/section-08-final-cta.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"> <img src=\"/brand/images/section-08-final-cta.png\" alt=\"Final CTA brand reference\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>Final CTA</span> </a> </div> </section> <section class=\"brand-assets-panel wide downloads-panel\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">Files</p> <div class=\"download-grid\"> <a href=\"/brand/logo-mark.svg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Logo mark</a><a href=\"/brand/logo-horizontal.svg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Horizontal logo</a><a href=\"/brand/color-palette.svg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Color palette SVG</a><a href=\"/brand/brand-tokens.json\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Brand tokens JSON</a><a href=\"/brand/design-tokens.css\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Design tokens CSS</a><a href=\"/brand/profitslocal-design.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Original design MD</a> </div> </section> </div> </section>  </main> <footer class=\"site-footer\"> <div class=\"footer-inner\"> <div class=\"footer-brand\"> <img src=\"/brand/logo-horizontal.svg\" alt=\"profitslocal\"> <h2>Local websites, built before you buy.</h2> <p class=\"lede\">Free website previews for local businesses.</p> <p class=\"micro\">&copy; 2026 profitslocal. profitslocal.com</p> </div> <div class=\"footer-list\"> <h3>Site</h3> <a href=\"/#pricing\">Pricing</a> <a href=\"/#faq\">FAQ</a> <a href=\"/#contact\">Contact</a> <a href=\"/brand-assets\">Brand assets</a> <a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a> <a href=\"/cases\">Cases</a> </div> <div class=\"footer-list\"> <h3>Support</h3> <a href=\"mailto:hi@profitslocal.com\">hi@profitslocal.com</a> <a href=\"/#contact\">Request a free pre-build</a> <a href=\"/#faq\">Domain setup</a> </div> <div class=\"footer-list footer-social\"> <h3>Social</h3> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@profitslocal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">YouTube</a><a href=\"https://x.com/profitslocal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">X</a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/profitslocal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profitslocal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Facebook</a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/profitslocal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Instagram</a> </div> </div> </footer> </div> </body></html>","isError":false}

